{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We can hardly see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My sister, Laura, and I ran into the church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And as we went into the church, the statue of Jesus Christ by the altar was standing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that hysterical-- state of hysteria, we threw ourselves in front of that statue, screaming, Jesus, Jesus, help us, help us, crying because we would have prayed to Allah, even though Jewish people believe only in the invisible God.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But driven by fear, we turned to Jesus Christ for help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we dragged our bundles away from the altar on the side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we laid there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I ret-- retreat to another, which I forgot to mention?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war, our children obtained a puppy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we children were thinking, what should we name that puppy?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard of names-- Nero, Caesar, another tyrant of history.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew Hitler's our enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's a dog.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So children said, we'll call him Hitler, then like it's, it's an insult to Hitler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We called him, Hitler, Hitler!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we realized that the puppy was very affectionate, licking our faces. kiss-- we were kissing him on the mouth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said, don't kiss the dog on the mouth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He licks everything in the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We loved him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we realized, how could we call a pet that we loved Hitler?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We can't-- we cannot kiss him and call him Hitler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we changed it to Rex.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a Ukrainian population who-- Polish citizens, but they were enemies to Poland because that territory, Eastern Poland, was Ukraine once.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the Poles conquered it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they prayed and hoped that someday, they'll retrieve that land.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the breadbasket of Poland, very rich land.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
